---
title: Cal Smart Harissa Salmon and Chickpea Stew with Buttered Ciabatta
description: Smoky and complex North African spices are combined with chili-garlic sauce to infuse this dish with intense flavours. Ciabatta points are perfect dippers for this visually appealing and wholesome stew!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/ragout-de-saumon-et-de-pois-chiches-au-harissa-85ed79e3.jpg
